14[4signs you are having a bad day14] Your manager calls you into the office on a Friday.
14[4signs you are having a bad day14] Every job lead at Lockheed leads to people who are always at offsite/getting the business/CI/etc meetings
14[4signs you are having a bad day14] Every person you ask for job leads says;"I wish *I* had some job leads"
14[4signs you are having a bad day14] People you talk to outside of Lockheed say,"You could try company ABC. Oh, but they laid off 25% of their people 3 months ago."
14[4signs you are having a bad day14] Fellow co-workers on AFR talk *seriously* about jobs at K-Mart.
14[4signs you are having a bad day14] People in your department greet each other with "How's the job search?" instead of "How's it going?"
